
  Salamence    Dragon Type Pokémon

  SALAMENCE came about as a result 
  of a strong, long-held dream 
  of growing wings.  It is said 
  that this powerful desire triggered 
  a sudden mutation in Salamence’s 
  cells, causing it to sprout its 
  magnificent wings. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Bagon ► Shelgon ► Salamence

